        {
            "id": "8b1c7f90238149f89bec8",
            "questionText": "In a football game, a $!$110 \\text{ kg}$!$ running back moving eastward at $!$8 \\text{ m/s}$!$ is tackled by a $!$95 \\text{ kg}$!$ linebacker moving westward at $!$7 \\text{ m/s}$!$. Upon impact, the two players collide and stick together, moving as a single unit. Determine the final velocity (magnitude and direction) of the combined players immediately after the tackle.",
            "imageText": "",
            "steps": [
                {
                    "id": "49eaf8cc0b7b4f29b7dba",
                    "stepText": "Let's start by identifying the correct formula to calculate a body's momentum. Which of the following formulas correctly represents momentum?",
                    "stepText2": "",
                    "stepImage": "",
                    "stepSolveAnswer": [
                        ""
                    ],
                    "stepSolveAnswerUnits": "",
                    "stepConcepts": [
                        "cb2fb9ab-0661-426b-8ed1-18f42da83312"
                    ],
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "optionText": "$!$p=mv$!$",
                            "optionImage": "",
                            "isCorrect": true
                        },
                        {
                            "optionText": "$!$p=m+v$!$",
                            "optionImage": "",
                            "isCorrect": false
                        },
                        {
                            "optionText": "$!$p=\\frac{m}{v}$!$",
                            "optionImage": "",
                            "isCorrect": false
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "92148d1a3d1f439c80559",
                    "stepText": "Great! Now, calculate the momentum of the running back who has a mass of $!$110 \\text{ kg}$!$ and is moving eastward at $!$8 \\text{ m/s}$!$ (remember to use the appropriate sign for eastward).",
                    "stepText2": "",
                    "stepImage": "",
                    "stepSolveAnswer": [
                        "880"
                    ],
                    "stepSolveAnswerUnits": "kg\u00b7m/s",
                    "stepConcepts": [
                        "cb2fb9ab-0661-426b-8ed1-18f42da83312"
                    ],
                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "41c563558eb5468d992cc",
                    "stepText": "Next, calculate the momentum of the linebacker who has a mass of $!$95 \\text{ kg}$!$ and is moving westward at $!$7 \\text{ m/s}$!$ (ensure you assign the correct sign for the westward direction).",
                    "stepText2": "",
                    "stepImage": "",
                    "stepSolveAnswer": [
